  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The project team developped and validated a French patient-based health-related quality of
      life instrument in kidney transplant: the QoL Retrans.

      The aim of the study is to determine the minimum significant change of the valdiated tool:
      ReTransQol
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
